name: Reach the Cube Club
description:
Reach the Cube Club - 3D-platformer game, that was gently made by me firstly for a jam, and now i want to share it with you!

It's a very simple and cute platformer you would like, if you like pretty 3d graphics, female japaneese voice, and platforming genre.

Hope you'll like it! Enjoy.

Credits: 

japaneese voice generator: https://ttsmp3.com/text-to-speech

sound effects: https://freesound.org/

Tools i used to develop this game: Unity3d, Blender

If you liked this game, please, consider yourself to support my game development by donating some money. Thanks!
